        "description": "Three-level mesh refinement study (coarse/medium/fine: ~45k, ~180k, ~720k elements) demonstrates <2% change in all three QoIs (stiffness, yield force, force at 40 mm) between medium and fine meshes; Richardson extrapolation GCI < 3% for all QoIs."
