      },
      "rationale": "All model inputs are traceable to measured data from the specific material lot and manufacturing batch used in the bench constructs. Material property uncertainty is propagated through a Monte Carlo analysis (n=1000 draws) confirming that input variability contributes <4% to QoI uncertainty, within the accepted budget. Geometry inputs are verified against CMM measurements of three representative constructs."
