      "rationale": "The selected QoIs are the exact metrics specified in FDA guidance for ASTM F1717 pedicle screw submissions. Construct stiffness characterizes the elastic response; yield force identifies the onset of permanent deformation; force at 40 mm displacement characterizes post-yield energy absorption. These QoIs are directly relevant to the COU decision (whether FEA can substitute for or supplement bench testing in the regulatory submission) and are not surrogates."
